06:57.985 --> 07:01.486
- I meant what do you
think of me physically?

07:01.488 --> 07:03.488
- Physically?
- Mm.

07:05.558 --> 07:07.626
- I'm not really, um.

07:07.628 --> 07:10.495
- Be candid, Moses.

07:10.497 --> 07:11.696
- Candid?

07:11.698 --> 07:13.131
- Very.

07:15.701 --> 07:17.602
- I'm not really comfortable.

07:17.604 --> 07:18.970
- Who's comfortable?

07:18.972 --> 07:20.872
Just be honest.

07:20.874 --> 07:23.508
- What, do I think you're
a good-looking woman?

07:23.510 --> 07:24.509
- Yes.

07:24.511 --> 07:26.111
- I mean, yeah.

07:26.113 --> 07:30.615
- But uglier than
women your age.

07:30.617 --> 07:34.886
I'm a good piece of fruit
too long in the fridge.

07:34.888 --> 07:37.088
- That's, isn't that, like.

07:37.090 --> 07:39.991
- But good-looking enough.

07:39.993 --> 07:42.861
At least as I sit here across
from you in what appears

07:42.863 --> 07:47.833
to be some kind of
impenetrable Artemis state,

07:47.835 --> 07:50.502
