the last outer crust

07:59.847 --> 08:02.647
of our prettiness
left, and that can be

08:02.649 --> 08:06.685
combined with haughtiness
or real superiority.

08:06.687 --> 08:10.689
Until a young man badly wants
to break that outer crust.

08:10.691 --> 08:12.924
He wants to prove this and that

08:12.926 --> 08:15.126
to himself, and
the middle-aged woman.

08:15.128 --> 08:17.128
But you see,
the woman's unwise if she

08:17.130 --> 08:18.897
allows herself to be stripped.

08:18.899 --> 08:21.533
The thing about Artemis is that,

08:21.535 --> 08:24.102
is that her nakedness in
the pool in the woods,

08:24.104 --> 08:27.506
when Actaeon sees her, yes?

08:27.508 --> 08:28.907
- Um, yeah.

08:28.909 --> 08:31.109
- Her nakedness
is not just a myth

08:31.111 --> 08:33.111
about the virginity of maidens.

08:33.113 --> 08:35.780
It's a myth also
about the final,

08:35.782 --> 08:39.650
brittle sex appeal
of older women.

08:43.188 --> 08:45.724
If you were to see me naked,

08:45.726 --> 08:48.527
like Actaeon,
you would have to die.

08:55.234 --> 08:58.537
You're a mature man, correct?

08:58.539 --> 09:00.171
- Yeah.

09:00.173 --> 09:02.674
- You're not one of
these immature fumblers,

09:02.676 --> 09:07.312
