for my birthday last year.

17:28.248 --> 17:31.249
- Hm, I think what you
and your museum-going self

17:31.251 --> 17:34.752
and your third self are missing
is a purposeful negation.

17:34.754 --> 17:37.455
This is apparently
counterintuitive.

17:37.457 --> 17:39.490
Okay.

17:39.492 --> 17:43.461
Purposefulness would seem to
have a positive component, yes?

17:43.463 --> 17:46.230
It positively is negation.

17:46.232 --> 17:49.133
But here's where I might
take issue with my own poem.

17:49.135 --> 17:51.702
Negation positively is negation,

17:51.704 --> 17:53.671
but only within
a conceptual system,

17:53.673 --> 17:57.442
the perhaps a priori system
of logical coherence.

17:57.444 --> 18:00.778
So what I'm doing
isn't really writing,

18:00.780 --> 18:04.449
but unwriting, you see?

18:04.451 --> 18:08.486
My negation has no positive
aspect, it simply isn't.

18:08.488 --> 18:10.288
- That's marvelous.

18:11.590 --> 18:13.524
- Thank you.

18:13.526 --> 18:16.227
- Did you really say my negation

18:16.229 --> 18:18.763
